      "comment": "STEEL STRIDE (9) made a nice return at his latest appearance five days ago, finishing 14 metres away in third over 1609m at Menangle. Drawn to enjoy a cosy run but might need things to go his way at some stage. Leading hope in a similar race. CREDO STRIDE (5) was responsible for a very good effort last time over 1770m at this track, finishing second and just a head from the winner. Stepping up a level this time but on his best form he is good enough to take this out. KALYPSO RAINBOW (11) is next in line and although she has to contend with an awkward gate a win is not out of the question. MY ULTIMATE FRANCO NZ (10) cannot be ruled out but needs a bit of luck from the tricky draw.",
